There is a long and wide ground, Friday prayers are also offered in the mosque, which is from a very old time, there is a Meo hostel in the mosque premises itself, in which free facilities have been provided for the students studying in various schools and colleges of the Muslim community. Sadar also lives here, there are various shops around the mosque especially beds, mattresses, coolers, fans, cupboards, chairs, grain tanks, clothes, e-friends, and a branch of State Bank of India is also present.
